-- All of my scripts owe a debt to Sal Soghoian - sal@mac.com
-- Caution: Manipulatiing presenter nortes via AppleScript will 
-- remove text styling: bold, italics, underline, color, etc. 
-- will all be removed from the resulting text.
--
-- TODO: should be turned into a droplet to handle multiple decks
-- Currenly only impacts the frontmost presentation
--

tell application "Keynote"
	
	tell document 1
		-- set font name here
		
		set font of presenter notes of every slide to "Helvetica"
		
		- set text size here
		
		set size of presenter notes of every slide to 18
	end tell
end tell

